{"title_page": "2020 Tajik Super Cup", "text_new": "{{Infobox football match\n| title              = 2020 Tajik Super Cup\n| other_titles       = \n| image              = \n| event              = [[Tajikistan Super Cup]]\n| team1              = [[FC Istiklol|Istiklol]]\n| team1score         = 2\n| team2              = [[FK Khujand|Khujand]]\n| team2score         = 1\n| details            = \n| date               = 4 April 2020\n| stadium            = [[Pamir Stadium]]\n| city               = [[Dushanbe]]\n| referee            = Nasrullo Kabirov ([[Nurak]])<ref name=\"Referee\"/>\n| attendance         = 0<ref name=\"Behind Closed Doors\"/>\n| weather            = \n| previous           = [[2019 Tajik Super Cup|2019]]\n| next               = [[2021 Tajik Super Cup|2021]]\n}}\nThe '''2020 Tajik Supercup''' was the 11th [[Tajikistan Super Cup]], an annual Tajik [[association football|football]] match played between the winners of the previous season's [[Tajikistan Higher League]] and [[Tajikistan Cup]]. The match was contested by 2019 [[2019 Tajikistan Higher League|League]] and [[2019 Tajikistan Cup|Cup]] champions [[FC Istiklol|Istiklol]], and the league runners-up [[FK Khujand|Khujand]]. It was held at the [[Pamir Stadium]] in [[Dushanbe]] on 4 April.\n\n==Background==\nOn 27 March, the [[Tajikistan Football Federation]] announce that the opening round of games would be played behind closed doors due to the threat of the [[2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic]],<ref name=\"Behind Closed Doors\">{{cite web |title=\u041c\u0410\u0422\u0427 \u0417\u0410 \u0421\u0423\u041f\u0415\u0420\u041a\u0423\u0411\u041e\u041a \u0422\u0410\u0414\u0416\u0418\u041a\u0418\u0421\u0422\u0410\u041d\u0410-2020 \u0418 \u0418\u0413\u0420\u042b \u0427\u0415\u041c\u041f\u0418\u041e\u041d\u0410\u0422\u0410 \u0411\u0423\u0414\u0423\u0422 \u041f\u0420\u041e\u0425\u041e\u0414\u0418\u0422\u042c \u0411\u0415\u0417 \u0417\u0420\u0418\u0422\u0415\u041b\u0415\u0419 |url=http://fft.tj/match-za-superkubok-tadzhikistana-2020-i-igry-chempionata-budut-prohodit-bez-zritelej/ |website=fft.tj |publisher=Tajikistan Football Federation |accessdate=27 March 2020 |language=Russian |date=27 March 2020}}</ref> with referee Nasrullo Kabirov being confirmed as the match official on 1 April.<ref name=\"Referee\">{{cite web |title=\u041d\u0410\u0421\u0420\u0423\u041b\u041b\u041e \u041a\u0410\u0411\u0418\u0420\u041e\u0412 \u0420\u0410\u0421\u0421\u0423\u0414\u0418\u0422 \u0418\u0421\u0422\u0418\u041a\u041b\u041e\u041b \u0418 \u00ab\u0425\u0423\u0414\u0416\u0410\u041d\u0414\u00bb \u0412 \u041c\u0410\u0422\u0427\u0415 \u0417\u0410 \u0421\u0423\u041f\u0415\u0420\u041a\u0423\u0411\u041e\u041a \u0422\u0410\u0414\u0416\u0418\u041a\u0418\u0421\u0422\u0410\u041d\u0410-2020 |url=http://fft.tj/nasrullo-kabirov-rassudit-istiklol-i-hudzhand-v-matche-za-superkubok-tadzhikistana-2020/ |website=fft.tj |publisher=Tajikistan Football Federation |accessdate=1 April 2020 |language=Russian |date=3 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Match details==\n{{football box\n|date       = 4 April 2020\n|time       = 17:00 ([[UTC+05:00|UTC+5]])\n|team1      = [[FC Istiklol|Istiklol]]\n|team2      = [[FK Khujand|Khujand]]\n|score      = 2-1\n|report     = \n|goals1     = [[Manuchekhr Dzhalilov|M.Dzhalilov]] {{goal|77}} <br> [[Muhammadjon Rakhimov|Rakhimov]] {{goal|78}}\n|goals2     = Sanjar Rixsiboev {{goal|2}}\n|stadium    = [[Pamir Stadium]], [[Dushanbe]]\n|attendance = 0<ref name=\"Behind Closed Doors\"/>\n|referee    = Nasrullo Kabirov ([[Nurak]])<ref name=\"Referee\"/>\n|}}\n{| width=92%\n|-\n|{{Football kit\n |pattern_la = \n |pattern_b  = \n |pattern_ra = \n |pattern_sh = _collarwhite\n |pattern_so = _3_stripes_red\n |leftarm    = FF0000\n |body       = FF0000\n |rightarm   = FF0000\n |shorts     = 000000\n |socks      = 000000\n |title      = Istiklol\n}}\n|{{Football kit\n |pattern_la = \n |pattern_b  = \n |pattern_ra = \n |pattern_sh = \n |pattern_so = \n |leftarm    = 0000FF\t\n |body       = 0000FF\t\n |rightarm   = 0